#: src/setup/windows.md
msgid "**Resource limits.** Docker Desktop on Windows allocates RAM/CPU via `%USERPROFILE%\\.wslconfig`, which defaults to half host RAM. The full configuration surface is documented in Microsoft's [Advanced settings configuration in WSL](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/wsl/wsl-config) reference. A reasonable starting envelope for a single-user ZeroClaw deployment is:"
