#: src/foundations/fnd-004-engineering-infrastructure.md
msgid "**Reusable workflow**: A GitHub Actions workflow that can be called as a job from another workflow, with parameters. Allows build, test, and security logic to be defined once and called from both the PR pipeline and the release pipeline."
