#: src/foundations/fnd-005-contribution-culture.md
msgid "Architecture disagreements are healthy. They mean people care about how the system is built and are paying attention to the decisions being made. A team where nobody disagrees is not a team where everyone agrees. It is a team where people have stopped engaging."
