msgid "Extract the agent orchestration loop, CLI channel, security policy, plugin host, and IPC API into `crates/zeroclaw-runtime`, gated by the `agent-runtime` feature. This crate depends on `zeroclaw-api` and the foundation crates. It has no knowledge of Telegram, Discord, Anthropic, or any specific tool implementation."
