#: src/providers/routing.md
msgid "Runtime switches are session/runtime state. They do not edit `config.toml`; persisted defaults require an explicit config write. For tool-driven switches, bare provider family names such as `openai` are not switch targets because they do not identify which configured profile, credential, endpoint, or compatibility mode should be used."
