#: src/agents/history-management.md
msgid "The `history_pruning.*` config keys are reused as-is; `collapse_tool_results` and `keep_recent` no longer drive any code path (the most recent whole turn is kept structurally). The key idents are scheduled to be renamed at config schema V4 and are intentionally left in place until then."
