msgid "These env vars decide _where_ the config file and instance data live, before any `Config` exists. They keep their UPPERCASE form so the case rule disambiguates them from the schema-mirror surface. They resolve in the order `ZEROCLAW_CONFIG_DIR` > `ZEROCLAW_DATA_DIR` > `ZEROCLAW_WORKSPACE` (deprecated):"
