#: src/channels/acp.md
msgid "ZeroClaw also accepts inbound `session/update` (and the legacy `session/event` alias) notifications from the client for custom event injection. Not in the base ACP spec: ZeroClaw-specific. If the ACP spec later defines an inbound `session/update` with different semantics, this will be renamed `_meta/session/update`."
