#: src/setup/windows.md
msgid "ZeroClaw publishes a Linux container image at **`ghcr.io/zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw:latest`** (and `:vX.Y.Z` for tagged releases). On Windows, run it via Docker Desktop or via `sudo apt install docker.io` inside a WSL distro; both work, and the container behaviour is identical."
